<div align="center"><h1>EQ Everquest Illusionist's Pantaloons</h1></div><br /><div align="center"><table class="classicview" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td class="classictitle" valign="top" height="14">
Illusionist's Pantaloons
</td></tr><tr valign="top"><td valign="top"><table border="0" width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td class="classicdata">MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <br /><img src="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/images/items/item_635.gif" height="40" width="40" align="right" alt="Illusionist's Pantaloons" />Slot: <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/armor/legs/" title="Legs">LEGS</a><br />AC: 7<br />STA: +5 CHA: +4 INT: +2 HP: +20 MANA: +50 <br />SV FIRE +2 SV COLD +2 SV DISEASE +1 SV MAGIC +3 SV POISON +1 <br />Effect: <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/spells/clarity-id174.php" title="Clarity">Clarity</a> (Must Equip, Casting Time: 15.0 Seconds)<br />WT: 0.5 Size: MEDIUM<br />Class: <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/classes-enchanter.php" title="Enchanter">ENC</a>&nbsp;<br />Race: <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-human.php" title="Human">HUM</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-erudite.php" title="Erudite">ERU</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-highelf.php" title="High Elf">HIE</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-darkelf.php" title="Dark Elf">DEF</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-gnome.php" title="Gnome">GNM</a>&nbsp;<br />Slot 1, Type 7: empty<br /></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br /><hr width="95%" /><br /></div><div style="float: left; width: 50%;"><div class="itemimage" style="width: 50px; float:left;"><img src="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/images/items/item_635.gif" height="40" width="40" alt="Illusionist's Pantaloons" /></div><div style="float: left; text-transform: uppercase;"><b>Magic Item</b><br /><b>No Drop</b><br /></div><br style="clear: left" /><b>Item Type:</b> Armor<br /><b>Slots:</b> <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/armor/legs/" title="Legs">Legs</a><br /><b>Weight:</b> 0.5&nbsp;<b>Size:</b> Medium<br /><b>Price:</b> 1 cp<br /><b>Material Type:</b> Velious Leather 2<br /><br /><b>Armor Class:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">7</span><br /><b>Effect:</b> <img src="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/images/spells/spell_21.small.gif" border="0" alt="Clarity" width="10" height="10" />&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/spells/clarity-id174.php" title="Clarity">Clarity</a> (Must Equip)<br /><b>Cast Time:</b> <span style="color: #FF0000;">15.0</span> Seconds<br /><br /><b>HP:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+20</span><br /><b>Mana:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+50</span><br /><b>Charisma:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+4</span><br /><b>Intelligence:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+2</span><br /><b>Stamina:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+5</span><br /><br /><b>Cold Resist:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+2</span><br /><b>Disease Resist:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+1</span><br /><b>Fire Resist:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+2</span><br /><b>Magic Resist:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+3</span><br /><b>Poison Resist:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+1</span><br /><br /><b>Effect Level:</b> 50<br /><br /><b>Augmentation Slot 1:</b> Type 7<br /><br /><b>Last Updated:</b> January 13, 2004 - 9:33 am<br /><br /><b>Illusionist's Pantaloons is available for purchase at <a href="http://wetrack.it/yantis/af.cgi?aid=919&redirect=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mysupersales.com%2Fsearch.asp%3Fq%3DIllusionist's%2BPantaloons%26server%3D-1">MySuperSales</a></b><br /><br /><b>Platinum is also for sale at <a href="http://wetrack.it/yantis/af.cgi?aid=919&redirect=http://www.mysupersales.com/">MySuperSales</a></b><br /></div><div style="margin-left: 50%;";><b>Classes:</b><ul><li><a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/classes-enchanter.php" title="Enchanter">Enchanter</a></li></ul><b>Races:</b><ul><li><a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-human.php" title="Human">Human</a></li><li><a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/races-erudite.php" title="Erudite">Erudite</a></li><li><a href